 * Interested in partaking in an User Schema demo with some of our team? We want your feedback in elevating  Zitadel’s product journey, reach out to Jim.Morrison@Zitadel.com to learn more!
 * Meet with our Community team and share your experiences leveraging Zitadel and what we can improve. Feel free to schedule time here [https://calendar.app.google/UgTzLndLKKMk7BYp8]!

